column1: # This file is adapted from P. Barbier's constellation boundary file:
# which in turn is based on the machine-readable version of E. Delporte's
# are arranged in continuous counterclockwise order.  Columns are:
# RA is vertex right ascension in decimAql hours (B1875)
# Dec is vertex declination in decimAql degrees (B1875)
# Con is IAU abbreviation of constellation for vertex
# Serpens Cauda and Serpens Caput are abbreviated Ser1 and Ser2
